<plot>Abigail Alexander is facetious, demanding, and unrelentingly English. Her life as a student in Dublin is, if not up to her high standards, at least tolerable. But then her Irish boyfriend 'does her wrong'. He loses his hat. The one that made him look hot. And nobody else seems to really appreciate the gravity of the situation. So Abigail Alexander gets her cricket bat and proceeds to mete out justice, to make things, if not exactly right, at least tolerable.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?055997</url></doc>
